title: Calisthenics workout routines PDF book - 2nd Edition
description:
This guide contains remedial workout programs and routines for beginners through advanced athletes. Bodyweight only bodybuilding programs are also covered, such as a golden age style program and a daily double split based loosely on routines performed by competitive bodybuilders. Training tactics for each style of workout (skill, strength, bodybuilding), deload protocols, and recommended training frequencies are included. You can add sandbags or kettlebells to many of the exercises to make them even harder.

For more resources -
 
http://www.oddobjecttraining.com
